A cyberpunk-style digital landscape showing a complex network of glowing fiber optic cables and data streams flowing through a dark cityscape, with some pathways fractured, tangled, or blocked by ominous red barriers and corrupted nodes. Diagnostic holographic panels float in the air displaying network topology maps and signal wave patterns. The scene features a lone figure in a hooded jacket crouched on a rooftop, using a handheld device that projects ethereal blue scanning beams into the chaotic web of connections below. Neon Singapore-inspired architecture looms in the background with rain streaking down. The color palette emphasizes electric blues, deep purples, warning oranges, and harsh magentas against an inky black sky. The overall mood conveys troubleshooting and investigation within a broken digital infrastructure.
